{% section "Agent Instructions" %}
**Add follow-up tasks discovered during work:**
```bash
python3 ~/.claude/hooks/state/queue_ops.py add \
  --goal "..." --priority MED --source [agent-type] --project [project]
```

**Leave discoveries for other sessions:**
```bash
python3 ~/.claude/hooks/state/drops.py write \
  --to all --type DISCOVERY --payload "..."
```

**Write scratchpad before returning:**
File: `.claude/memory/scratch-$SESSION_ID.md`
Minimum: one `<!-- MEM -->` block with OBSERVATION or FLAG.
{% endsection %}

